e certificate that the training is necessary for the performance of the POP.</li><li>The training course lasts at least 32 hours.</li><li>The training provider must be registered as a qualified service provider. If, on 31 August 2019 at the latest, the training provider was recognised as a service provider for the SME portfolio or for training vouchers, it will be considered a qualified service provider until 2 September 2021. From 2 September 2021, only the WSE quality registration will be valid.</li><li>The career certificate may not be older than 6 years.</li><li>You should attach the career certificate and the training enrolment certificate to your application.</li></ul></li></ul></li></ul>"
